    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1447886/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            中国古车舆名物考辨的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1378993">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1378993/" class="title-link">古代战车马尾为何要打个结？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1378993"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2330375/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2330375-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2330375/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">考拉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-05-13"
      class="main-meta">2008-05-13 01:15:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1378993_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  前几天，和几个学友去广东省博物馆参观湖北九连墩战国墓地所出土的文物时，有位学友提出，为什么在战车名物制度的示意图中，马尾总是打结的？这倒是我疏忽的问题，自然也就只有张口结舌的份儿。惭愧的是，我也去过兵马俑看过，何以就从来没有注意到这个细节呢？几个人就在那里...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1378993/#comments">(37回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">81有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1378993_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1378993_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
